import React from 'react'
import {  Box, Grid } from '@mantine/core'

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Box h={30}></Box>
    <Grid>
      <Grid.Col span={4}>1</Grid.Col>
      <Grid.Col span={4}>2</Grid.Col>
      <Grid.Col span={4}>3</Grid.Col>
    </Grid>
    </>
  )
}

export default Home
